title: Eureka NEU10AE5 Powerful Bagless Upright Vacuum Cleaner Carpet and Floor, AirSpeed Ultra-Lightweight Vacuum Cleaner, w/ Replacement Filter, Blue
description: We know you value a clean home and Eureka is proud to offer whole home cleaning solutions to make life a little easier.

This upright vacuum is the ultimate cleaning tool for any home! With its lightweight design and powerful suction, this vacuum can handle messes on hardwood floors, low-pile carpets, and car interiors. Its compact size allowing for easy storage makes it essential for apartment living.

The wide nozzle, crevice tool and dusting brush makes it a breeze to clean hard-to-reach areas like ceilings, upholstery, windows, lampshades, and furniture. Portable attachments, large dust cup and washable filter mean less time emptying and more time cleaning.

This efficient and cheap handheld vacuum is the perfect dust cleaner for any household! Don't let dust take over your space - upgrade to our Eureka Airspeed compact bagless upright vacuum and experience the ultimate cleaning experience today!
If you have any questions, contact our customer service team at 1-800-282-2886.
Warning: When using the vacuum cleaner, the floor brush may be clogged by hairs and dirt. We recommend cleaning the roller brush and the belt every 2 weeks.
Long-term failure to clean may cause malfunction, or even risk of smoke and belt broken.
